<%- @page_title = 'Tools & Resources' -%>

<%= render partial: 'shared/contextual_header', locals: {page_title: @page_title, parent_pages: []} %>

<div class="usa-section main-section tools-resources">
  <h1><%= @page_title %></h1>

  <div class="usa-grid tools-links">
    <ul class="usa-unstyled-list usa-width-one-half tools-list">
      <li>
        <%= link_to weight_estimator_path do %>
          <%= image_tag 'icons/weight-estimator.svg', alt: '', role: 'presentation' %>
          Household Goods Weight Estimator
        <% end %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= link_to offices_path do %>
          <%= image_tag 'icons/office-locator.svg', alt: '', role: 'presentation' %>
          PPPO &amp; Weight Scale Locations
        <% end %>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="usa-unstyled-list usa-width-one-half tools-list">
      <li>
        <%= link_to page_path('resources/inventory-form') do %>
          <%= image_tag 'icons/inventory-form.svg', alt: '', role: 'presentation' %>
          Self-Inventory Form
        <% end %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= link_to '#TODO' do %>
          <%= image_tag 'icons/ppm-estimator.svg', alt: '', role: 'presentation' %>
          PPM Reimbursement Estimator
        <% end %>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="resources-links">
    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <%= image_tag 'logos/military_one_source_logo.svg' %>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <h4><%= link_to 'Military One Source', 'https://www.militaryonesource.mil/' %></h4>
        <p>Military One Source has a bunch of articles about how to plan your move, find housing and employement in your new location, and how to deal with the stress  caused from uprooting your family.</p>
        <ul class="usa-unstyled-list two-column-list">
          <li><%= link_to 'Master Your Move Guide', 'https://www.militaryonesource.mil/pcs', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Military Spouses’ Blog', 'https://blog-brigade.militaryonesource.mil/blogs/moving-2/', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Moving Benefits', 'http://www.militaryonesource.mil/web/mos/moving-benefits', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to '24/7 Family Support Line', 'https://www.militaryonesource.mil/web/mos/confidential-help', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Helping Your Kids Cope', 'https://www.militaryonesource.mil/web/mos/-/nine-ways-to-help-your-kids-cope-with-moving', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <%= image_tag 'logos/military_installations_logo.svg' %>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <h4><%= link_to 'Military Installations', 'http://www.militaryinstallations.dod.mil/' %></h4>
        <p>Everything you need to know about your new base including school districts, pet restrictions, and on-base contact infomation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <%= image_tag 'logos/sesame_street_logo.svg' %>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <h4><%= link_to 'PBS Kids Relocation Resources', 'http://sesamestreetformilitaryfamilies.org/topic/relocation/' %></h4>
        <p>Videos, worksheets, and tips to help prepare the youngest members of the family for the PCS process.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <h4>Household Goods Policies and Supplements</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <ul class="usa-unstyled-list">
          <li><%= link_to 'Joint Travel Regulation', 'http://www.defensetravel.dod.mil/site/travelreg.cfm', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Defense Travel Regulation', 'https://www.ustranscom.mil/dtr/', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Air Force Household Goods Supplement', 'http://static.e-publishing.af.mil/production/1/af_a4_7/publication/afi24-501/afi24-501.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Marine Corps Household Goods Supplement', 'https://www.move.mil/documents/dod/MCO_4600_39_19_AUG_2016.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Navy Household Goods Supplement', 'https://www.move.mil/documents/dod/NAVSUP_PUB_490_Rev5.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <h4>Lodging</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <ul class="usa-unstyled-list">
          <li><%= link_to raw("#{abbr_tag('dod')} Lodging"), 'http://www.dodlodging.net/', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Coast Guard Lodging Locations', 'https://www.dodlodging.com/html/coastguard.htm', class: "usa-external_link" %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="usa-grid">
      <div class="usa-width-one-third">
        <h4 id="forms">Forms</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="usa-width-two-thirds">
        <ul class="usa-unstyled-list">
          <li><%= link_to 'DD1791 - Counseling Checklist', 'http://www.esd.whs.mil/Portals/54/Documents/DD/forms/dd/dd1797.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %>: This form will be automatically generated by the Defense Personal Property system upon completion of self counseling.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'DD1299 - Application for Shipment and Storage', 'http://www.esd.whs.mil/Portals/54/Documents/DD/forms/dd/dd1299.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %>: This form will be automatically generated by the Defense Personal Property system upon completion of self counseling when you indicate storage is requested.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'DD2278 - Application for PPM (DITY) and Counseling Checklist', 'http://www.esd.whs.mil/Portals/54/Documents/DD/forms/dd/dd2278.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %>: This form will be automatically generated by the Defense Personal Property system upon completion of self counseling for a PPM.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'SF1038 - Advance of Funds Application (PPM)', 'https://app_gsagov_prod_rdcgwaajp7wr.s3.amazonaws.com/SF1038-77.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %>: This form needs to be completed and submitted to your local finance office if you will be requesting an advance of funds to help cover some of the expenses associated with your move.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'DD1351-2 - Travel Voucher', 'http://www.esd.whs.mil/Portals/54/Documents/DD/forms/dd/dd1351-2.pdf', class: "usa-external_link" %>: This form needs to be completed and submitted to your local finance office at the completion of your move so you can claim all your reimbursable expenses that you are entitled to during your move. Some finance offices have online systems for this form in place, however it’s listed here if needed.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'Sample Inconvenience Claim Letter', asset_path('claim.pdf'), download: 'claim.pdf' %>: Included is a sample inconvenience claim letter to use as an example. For more information on an Inconvenience claim, please review this <%= link_to 'Frequently Asked Question', faqs_path %>.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'PPM Submission Checklist', asset_path('ppm_checklist.pdf'), download: 'ppm_checklist.pdf' %>: The Personally Procured Move checklist will help you gather all the required documents prior to submitting your PPM voucher to the personal property office.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'ATF Form 6 (Active Duty Service Members Only)', 'https://www.atf.gov/firearms/docs/form/form-6-part-2-application-and-permit-importation-firearms-ammunition-and', class: 'usa-external_link' %>: This form is used by Active Duty Military members to apply to permanently import firearms, ammunition and implements of war into the United States.</li>
          <li><%= link_to 'ATF Form 6 (Civilians & Non-Active Duty Service Members)', 'https://www.atf.gov/firearms/docs/form/form-6-part-1-application-and-permit-importation-firearms-ammunition-and', class: 'usa-external_link' %>: This form is used by civilians and non-active duty service members apply to permanently import firearms, ammunition and implements of war into the United States.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
